---

<section class="site-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-inner">
      <h1 class="intro-headline">
        Small projects.<br />
        Strange ideas.<br />
        All interactive.
      </h1>
      <hr class="intro-rule" aria-hidden="true" />
      <p class="intro-body">
        ToyWebCreations is a collection of focused, playable web experiments —
        puzzles, simulations, generators, and visual curiosities.
        Each one exists because it was interesting to build.
        Pick something. Try it.
      </p>
      <p class="intro-scroll-hint">
        <span class="hint-char">↓</span> scroll to browse
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .site-intro {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0 var(--space-16);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .site-intro .container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .intro-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6.5vw, var(--text-7xl));
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    text-shadow: var(--text-deboss-strong);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .intro-rule {
    border: none;
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--phosphor-dim);
    margin: var(--space-8) auto;
  }

  .intro-body {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-10);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-scroll-hint {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .hint-char {
    animation: fadePulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  @keyframes fadePulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    50%       { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateY(3px); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hint-char {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
